The '''1961 [[Syracuse Orange football|Syracuse Orangemen football]] team''' represented [[Syracuse University]] in the 1961 NCAA University Division college football season. [[Running back]] [[Ernie Davis]] would become the first [[African American|black]] player to win the [[Heisman Trophy]].
